name: Safe Motherhood
title: Lowest Maternal Mortality Rate
description: In 2016, Czechia reported a maternal mortality ratio of just 1 per 100,000 live births, one of the lowest in the world, showcasing its exceptional healthcare system for mothers.

name: Manufacturing Hub
title: High Dependence on Manufactured Imports
description: By 2024, 83.68% of Czechia's merchandise imports were manufactured goods, indicating a strong reliance on global manufacturing networks to support its economy.
